#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:33
msgid ""
"Uniformize the `vtkPlot` API for color setters/getter, in order to fit the "
"API of `vtkPen` and `vtkBrush`. Methods using floating point parameters (e."
"g. `vtkPlot::SetColor(double r, double g, double b)`) are now suffixed with "
"`F` to avoid confusion with equivalent functions using unsigned chars. The "
"former ones are marked as deprecated."
