msgid "Added new `vtkPolyhedron::TriangulateFaces` method."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:338
msgid ""
"Added new `vtkStaticFaceHashLinksTemplate` templated class that can be used "
"to group faces of an unstructured grid and eliminates duplicates."
