msgid ""
"`vtkHyperTreeGrid` has a new type of cursor, called `unlimited` cursors. "
"`vtkHyperTreeGridNonOrientedUnlimitedMooreSuperCursor` and "
"`vtkHyperTreeGridNonOrientedUnlimitedGeometryCursor` have been added."
