msgid ""
"Add new `vtkNonLinearCell::StableClip` method and `vtkQuadraticTetra::"
"StableClip` implementation. The goal of this clip is to only decompose a "
"cell if its actually clipped, otherwise keep the non-linear cell in its "
"entirety. Note: this clipping approach will lead to topological holes "
"between decomposed cells and the remaining non-linear cells."
