#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:567
msgid ""
"Added ANSYS Fluent CFF Reader (Common Fluid Format) into its own dedicated "
"module `VTK::IOFLUENTCFF`, which currently supports the new "
"`vtkFLUENTCFFReader`. See further documentation [here][fluent-ccf-docs]."
