#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:570
msgid ""
"Added `vtkNumberToString::SetHighExponent` and `vtkNumberToString::"
"SetLowExponent` to control the exponent range for scientific or fixed "
"notation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:572
msgid "Fixed reading fault on vector fields with `vtkXMLHyperTreeGridReader`."
