#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:573
msgid ""
"Added support for mixed cell unstructured grids in `vtkConduitSource`. See "
"`ValidateMeshTypeMixed` and `ValidateMeshTypeMixed2D` tests in `IO/"
"CatalystConduit/Testing/Cxx/TestConduitSource.cxx` for more details."
