#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:587
msgid ""
"`vtkIOSSReader` can now merge entity blocks into a single block for the "
"exodus format using the flag `MergeExodusEntityBlocks` which is off by "
"default. This is useful e.g. for cases where the entity blocks just "
"represent different cell types but they actually describe the same block."
