#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:591
msgid ""
"Incorrect `vtkEnSightWriter` output has been fixed for `VTK_POLYGON`, "
"`VTK_WEDGE`, `VTK_QUADRATIC_WEDGE`, `VTK_QUADRATIC_EDGE` or "
"`VTK_CONVEX_POINT_SET` cell types. Support for `VTK_POLYHEDRON` has also "
"been added."
