#: ../../../../release/_9.3-stripped.md:857
msgid ""
"All VTK-m cmake targets are now prefixed with `vtkm_`. Exceptions have been "
"made for `vtkm::cuda` and `vtkm::kokkos_hip`, for compatibility with "
"external VTK-m imports."
